{"tid":2330834,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"16 歲男被控管有兩罐噴漆　獲撤控准簽保守行為　官斥控方推論無證據","createTime":"2020-12-18T10:18:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T12:01:05.000Z","uid":56115,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b2aa6140fe372c28eaabba0c24b931261ee7d6aa","tid":2330834,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:18:13.000Z","msg":"今年 1 月 19 日，民間集會在中環發起集會，其後演變成警民衝突。一名16歲男學生涉管有兩罐噴漆，被控管有物品意圖摧毀財產罪，案件今（22日）在東區裁判法院提堂，被告獲准以 1000 元簽保、守行為 12 個月，同意案情並撤回控罪。主任裁判官錢禮直斥，控方在沒有直接證據下，指被告有意圖破壞他人財產，明言法庭無法認同這個推論。"},{"pid":"cd2ac1452943c791c512e73f20f4c7cff69db701","tid":2330834,"uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:18:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/16-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%89%E5%85%A9%E7%BD%90%E5%99%B4%E6%BC%86-%E7%8D%B2%E6%92%A4%E6%8E%A7%E5%87%86%E7%B0%BD%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%88%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA-%E5%AE%98%E6%96%A5%E6%8E%A7%E6%96%B9%E6%8E%A8%E8%AB%96%E7%84%A1%E8%AD%89%E6%93%9A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F16-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%25BD%2590%25E5%2599%25B4%25E6%25BC%2586-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2592%25A4%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%2587%2586%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2588%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25A5%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%258E%25A8%25E8%25AB%2596%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2593%259A%2F&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrfno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=9f6a3465\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F16-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%25BD%2590%25E5%2599%25B4%25E6%25BC%2586-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2592%25A4%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%2587%2586%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2588%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E5%25AE%259